2000-10-18	Joel Sherrill <joel@OARcorp.com>

	* libc/fcntl.c: Do not require every filesystem to have an fcntl()
	handler.  Most fcntl() operations can be performed with no
	filesystem support.
	* ChangeLog: Corrected comment.

